twcore.core.events
Class SQLResultEvent

java.lang.Object
  twcore.core.events.SubspaceEvent
      twcore.core.events.SQLResultEvent

public class SQLResultEvent
extends SubspaceEvent

Event used to return the ResultSet of an SQL background query. All bots using SQL background queries must opt to handle this event.

setResultSet

public void setResultSet(java.sql.ResultSet set)
Sets the result set of this event to a specific ResultSet, and then handles the SQLResultEvent on the bot that made the query. If the identifier is null, then the event will not be handled. Called by SQLWorker.

Parameters:
set - Result set to assign to this event (may be null)
